Class SelfResetRepository

java.lang.Object
  control.Repository
      testCase.SelfResetRepository

public class SelfResetRepository
extends Repository

The SelfResetRepository class extends from Repository. It initialises the files and all HashMap in it as empty status. Namely, the SelfResetRepository class always reset all the attributes and files when it is created.
